cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DL

The paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques to automatically structure a set of terms into a taxonomy. This falls under the scope of computational linguistics (cs.CL) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The use of large quantities of text and heuristics also suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and deep learning (cs.DL) techniques.
